/*  Author Alexander Pitzer
    ETH Zurich
    Copyright (C) 2025 Alexander Pitzer

    Solubility equilibrium database and helper functions.
    Analogous structure to acidbase.mac.

    Database format: association list
      key = salt (string, mhchem-compatible)
      value = [pKsp, cation, cation_count, anion, anion_count]

    Ksp is always computed from pKsp: Ksp = 10^(-pKsp)
    This avoids rounding errors from storing both values.

    CRC Handbook of Chemistry and Physics — Table of solubility product constants
    NIST Standard Reference Database — Critically evaluated stability constants
    Lange's Handbook of Chemistry — Solubility product table
    Atkins' Physical Chemistry or Zumdahl's Chemistry textbook appendices
    IUPAC-NIST Solubility Data Series
*/

